Package: bubbler
Title: Generate relative abundance tables from amplicon-sequencing data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Zjardyn", "Liera-Hood", , "zlieraho@uwaterloo.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0857-6173"))
Description: Bubbler constructs relative abundance tables from various amplicon sequencing inputs. The tables can be modified, subsetted and rearranged. Finally, the tables can be plotted into stacked barcharts or bubble plots. 
